'''Odd Bakke II''' (2221-2304) was a Puerto Rican-French unemployed man.

== Early life (2221-2251) ==
Bakke was born in Ponce, Puerto Rico. He was the youngest of three brothers born to [[Tarjei Bakke V]] and his girlfriend Mariah Smith.

In 2239, Bakke moved to Oakland, California.

In 2251, Bakke emigrated to Lyon, France.

== Death ==
In 2304, Bakke died of old age.

== Relationships and children ==
From 2239 to 2251, Bakke dated a policewoman named Rachel Pringle (2221-after 2278). They had a son:

# Tarjei Bakke VII (2240-2309), museum worker
In 2251, Bakke started dating an exotic dancer named Celia Blanc (2228-2278). They had a daughter:

# Mila Bakke (2252-2341), policewoman
In 2278, Bakke started dating an unemployed woman named Eva Vega (2260-2350). They had a daughter:

# [[Celestina Bakke]]

